For Termux

pkg install git -y 
pkg install python -y 
chomod +x TBomb.sh
git clone https://github.com/sanketdon/TBombmod
cd TBomb
./TBomb.sh

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

For Debian-based GNU/Linux distributions

sudo apt install git
git clone https://github.com/sanketdon/TBombmod
cd TBomb
chomod +x TBomb.sh
bash TBomb.sh
